1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,080
I remember it made things worse.

2
00:00:02,080 --> 00:00:05,040
I remember figures appeared, restraining her mother,

3
00:00:05,040 --> 00:00:08,880
threatening the children, always demanding punishment.

4
00:00:08,880 --> 00:00:11,080
I remember the attacks grew more violent

5
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:13,280
as the moving day approached.

6
00:00:13,280 --> 00:00:14,800
I remember on the last night,

7
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:18,440
Kat and Sharon were told to leave the bedroom door open.

8
00:00:18,440 --> 00:00:20,880
I remember Sharon refused the top bunk.

9
00:00:20,880 --> 00:00:22,680
Finally, Kat gave in.

10
00:00:22,680 --> 00:00:24,720
I remember the house was quiet.

11
00:00:24,720 --> 00:00:26,280
I remember too quiet.

12
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:28,280
I remember then came the sound.

13
00:00:28,280 --> 00:00:30,560
I remember a slimy, slithering noise

14
00:00:30,560 --> 00:00:33,520
like something wet crawling across the floor.

15
00:00:33,520 --> 00:00:35,320
I remember Sharon screamed.

16
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,160
I remember Kat froze.

17
00:00:37,160 --> 00:00:38,880
I remember tentacle-like shapes

18
00:00:38,880 --> 00:00:40,320
shot from under the bed,

19
00:00:40,320 --> 00:00:42,640
wrapping around Sharon's ankles and wrists,

20
00:00:42,640 --> 00:00:44,440
trying to drag her under.

21
00:00:44,440 --> 00:00:47,760
I remember red eyes glowed from the darkness beneath.

22
00:00:47,760 --> 00:00:50,960
I remember her sisters sat paralyzed, unable to move.
